- Okay.

588
00:26:00,950 --> 00:26:02,343
[Tony chuckles]

589
00:26:02,386 --> 00:26:04,345
Yeah, get in there.

590
00:26:05,868 --> 00:26:06,956
Get in.

591
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,479
Stop, stop, stop.

592
00:26:12,005 --> 00:26:14,007
Come back.
Come back. Back up...

593
