594
00:26:18,446 --> 00:26:24,539
[metal clinking]

595
00:26:25,453 --> 00:26:26,802
Yeah.

596
00:26:26,846 --> 00:26:29,588
Okay. Okay.

597
00:26:30,110 --> 00:26:32,329
