676
00:30:11,331 --> 00:30:12,680
[Tony sighs]

677
00:30:14,290 --> 00:30:15,683
Oh, yeah.

678
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:18,033
<i>[Fred]: It is said...</i>

679
00:30:18,729 --> 00:30:20,557
