What the fuck are they doing?

732
00:32:20,895 --> 00:32:23,680
[indistinct reporting on TV]

733
00:32:23,724 --> 00:32:25,421
Hey, hey! Hey!

734
00:32:25,465 --> 00:32:28,424
Hey! I got lines rigged
